{"tid":1394642,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"疑誤當作忠旺 旺旺開市前曾遭拋售","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:35:52.000Z","uid":89046,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"654bb0f794add5a2dcba2551a54180c8138b7dff","tid":1394642,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>疑誤當作忠旺 旺旺開市前曾遭拋售</strong>   (12:44)<br />\n2019年8月1日<br />\n明報<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190801/s00010/f347d1f6a716467d1be54c08f2f44242.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190801%2Fs00010%2Ff347d1f6a716467d1be54c08f2f44242.jpg&h=c539df5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺旺(0151)今早開市前時段股價曾急挫，市場猜測可能有人誤將旺旺當作中國忠旺(1333)而沽售股票所致。<br />\n<br />\n根據彭博匯編的數據，旺旺在開市前交易時段開始時一度下跌7.8%，約10.1萬股股票以低位5.65元成交，不過，到常規交易時段開始時，股價拗腰回升，早段曾高見6.23元，最多升1.63%，中午收報6.2元，升1.14%。<br />\n<br />\n彭博指，旺旺股價突挫，可能與被稱為「烏龍指」的交易錯誤有關，也有人估計是「中國旺旺」與「中國忠旺」的中文名字中有三個字是相同，不排除有人沽錯對象。<br />\n<br />\n外電稍早報道，忠旺創始人劉忠田遭被美國聯邦大陪審團起訴，涉嫌與忠旺及數名被告，將大量鋁材走私至美國圖謀避近20億美元(156億港元)的關稅。忠旺股價上午急瀉，曾低見3.17元，下挫近21%，半日收報3.29元，挫19.96%。<br />\n<br />\n彭博向港交所(0388)以電子郵件查詢未獲回覆，旺旺在台北的營銷代表就股票波動亦不作評論。"},{"pid":"de549c10cba65c7f603e263cf32439d4a915502f","tid":1394642,"uid":112161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367b3a00683bb319855f738501f25b127a7619d0","tid":1394642,"uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f510f0678fc82377638d3c70a813126be988d9b4","tid":1394642,"uid":289708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a46d1c8b3816d5aa9bc7bd26a1bc8ab1d74e80","tid":1394642,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"擺到明有人借股票過數"},{"pid":"d86fc26e40d9f9bdbe7f696e7d55961a7c7941b9","tid":1394642,"uid":157676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87e416e674ed12bb9331ed10d39d054a341c61f","tid":1394642,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"假撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e5c2bd744ccf5abdf55a812e075e8c1a08d58a","tid":1394642,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"大拿拿幾億既野<br />\n會唔會搞錯呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68a7c66fbc5b4409fec66f939db5cdbd6f1091d","tid":1394642,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"唔怪得叫柯文哲出嚟爭，韓國瑜頭號fan屎無錢使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c6a1c9a189bfa5214404cc9e0b91a557fcecbd","tid":1394642,"uid":51790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:42:40.000Z","msg":"識唔識字呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6568dc5af3814d8169c773e9a98a1f575e815b16","tid":1394642,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"旺旺真鳩喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271eaa60a9ac3ad37ccf90d9b21c8ce0ae6ea2c8","tid":1394642,"uid":178365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:28:12.000Z","msg":"咁永旺呢？"},{"pid":"f23ea32eb18b904b8c6a96cafd4cd0800e65c8eb","ti